@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lpgtkq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos((v2 * (tmp + 0.66 + v0 + 0.39)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.01)) + wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = (v1 + tmp)
    v0 = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.58 * v2 + 0.37) + v2))
    tmp = wp.exp(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
